{
  "stem": "22447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know what, what she was doing there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I might have a vague idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'll come to that later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we brought her in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She looked like a film star-- blond hair, blue eyes, like made to measure for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So she, she came in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, can I see your pass?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she shows me a pass signed by the camp commandant giving the permission to go to [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Seelow, ?] to travel [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because she-- you had to, to go from one village to the other, you had to have a permit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Germans had to have a permit to go from one place to the other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I said, no, I don't want that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I want your SS card, [GERMAN], what they used to call it, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she gave me the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was about as big as a credit card-- a little bit bigger than a credit card.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Name, Irma Grese, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ober ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lieutenant, ?] born in 1923, I think she was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, hmm, I says, well, but we better keep her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because there was a regulation that all prisoners of war could be detained for 48 hours in transit.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you give them a tin of corned beef, like, for the transit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, well, we'll keep her for 48 hours and see if there-- there must be someone somewhere, all these thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she said, could she go back to her home to collect a few personal belongings, like a change of clothing, a comb, a brush, cosmetics.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She wasn't short of anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll take the receiver off.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
